age\"}}\n| {{nihongo|\"Feels Like Glass in the Gums\"|\u6b6f\u830e\u306b\u30ac\u30e9\u30b9|Haguki ni garasu}}\n| {{nihongo|\"Dazzling Dictatorship\"|\u307e\u3076\u3057\u304d\u72ec\u88c1|Mabushiki dokusai}}\n| {{nihongo|\"Ying and Yang Stripes\"|\u9670\u3068\u967d\u3001\u30b7\u30de\u30b7\u30de|In to y\u014d, shimashima}}\n| {{nihongo|\"On the Scent of the Holy Grail\"|\u8056\u676f\u306e\u5302\u3044|Seihai no nioi}}\n| {{nihongo|\"Camaraderie\"|\u4ef2\u9593\u306e\u8a3c\u3001\u6e29\u304b\u304f|Nakama no akashi, atatakaku|\"Warm Proof of Kinship\"}}\n| {{nihongo|\"Scorching Punishments\"|\u541b\u3092\u7126\u304c\u3059\u5236\u6b73|Kimi o kogasu seisai}}\n}}\n| Summary         = \n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber = 3\n | RelDate      = May 8, 2017<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.akitashoten.co.jp/comics/4253227562 |title=BEASTARS \u7b2c3\u5dfb |website=[[Akita Shoten]] |language=Japanese |accessdate=May 12, 2018 }}</ref>\n | ISBN         = 978-4-253-22756-8\n | LicensedRelDate = November 19, 2019<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.viz.com/read/manga/beastars-volume-3/product/6090 |title=BEASTARS Vol. 3 |publisher=[[Viz Media]] |accessdate=April 19, 2019}}</ref>\n | LicensedISBN = 978-1-9747-0800-0\n| ChapterListCol1 = \n{{Numbered list|start=17\n| {{nihongo|\"He Howls \"No\" Like a Child\"|\u9060\u5420\u3048\u306e\u30a4\u30e4\u30a4\u30e4\u75c7\u5019\u7fa4|T\u014dboe no Iya-Iya Sh\u014dk\u014dgun}}\n| {{nihongo|\"The Beasts' Summer Festival of the Meteor\"|\u7363\u306e\u76c6\u3001\u5f7c\u3089\u304c\u590f|Kemono no Bon, Karera ga Natsu}}\n| {{nihongo|\"The Name of the Howling Boy\"|\u30ac\u30a6\u30ac\u30a6\u541b\u306e\u540d\u306f|Gau-Gau Kimi no Na wa|\"Bow Wow Your Name\"}}\n| {{nihongo|\"The Client Next Door\"|\u96a3\u306e\u30af\u30e9\u30a4\u30a2\u30f3\u30c8|Tonari no Kuraianto}}\n| {{nihongo|\"Resonating with the Outside World\"|\u5916\u754c\u3068\u306e\u5171\u9cf4|Gaikai to no Ky\u014dmei}}\n| {{nihongo|\"Shadows of Tall Buildings\"|\u5efa\u3061\u4e26\u3076\u30d3\u