 Dream\"\n| \"The Old Year and the New Year of My Soul\"\n| \"The Howl of a Guardian Deity\"\n| \"You Are the Prince of Beasts\"\n| \"A Piece of Golden Hair On My Shirt, Now In My Pocket\"\n| \"Beast School Wars\"\n| \"A Drop of 18-Times Concentrate\"\n| \"I Give You My Crimson Cross Section\"\n| \"We Were Just Out Eating\"\n}}\n| Summary         = \n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber = 12\n | RelDate      = February 8, 2019<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.akitashoten.co.jp/comics/4253227651 |title=BEASTARS \u7b2c12\u5dfb |website=[[Akita Shoten]] |language=Japanese |accessdate=November 13, 2018 }}</ref>\n | ISBN         = 978-4-253-22765-0\n | LicensedRelDate = \u2014\n | LicensedISBN = \n| ChapterListCol1 = \n{{Numbered list|start=98\n| \"Meeting Eyes With Myself Twenty Years Into the Future\"\n| \"A Leader With a Black Mane\"\n| \"What Happens When You Bust a Tire In a Very Full Train?\"\n| \"Condition For Living: Raising a Stray Dog\"\n| \"Was It Fire That Made His Body Black?\"\n| \"Seeds Scatter Like Rain\"\n| \"A Lethal Dose of Love, Marmalade Flavored\"\n| \"Born to be Eaten\"\n| \"Scales that Reflect the Light of the Moon\"\n}}\n| Summary         = \n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber = 13\n | RelDate      = April 8, 2019<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.akitashoten.co.jp/comics/425322766X |title=BEASTARS \u7b2c13\u5dfb |website=[[Akita Shoten]] |language=Japanese |accessdate=July 21, 2019 }}</ref>\n | ISBN         = 978-4-253-22766-7\n | LicensedRelDate = \u2014\n | LicensedISBN = \n| ChapterListCol1 = \n{{Numbered list|start=107\n| \"Inherited Sanpaku Eyes that Determine the Fate of Love\"\n| \"Caribbean Neighborhood\"\n| \"An Oxygen-Depriving Date with a Merman\"\n| \"I Don't Know What Beer Tastes Like\"\n| \"His Marble-Like Eyes Are Blurred Like Frosted Glass\"\n| \"A Shower of Antitoxic Mist\"\n| \"A Body Filled with Purity and Whimsy\"\n| \"Friend, Shall I Bow Before You with My Tongue on the Floor?\"\n| \"Tonight, I Feel More Like a Bunny Than She Does (Now Dig In)\"\n}}\n| Summary         = \n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber = 14\n | RelDate      = July 8, 2019<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.akitashoten.co.jp/comics/4253227678 |title=BEASTARS \u7b2c14\u5dfb |website=[[Akita Shoten]] |language=Japanese |accessdate=July 21, 2019 }}</ref>\n | ISBN         = 978-4-253-22767-4\n | LicensedRelDate = \u2014\n | LicensedISBN = \n| ChapterListCol1 = \n{{Numbered list|start=116\n| \"A Dancing Boy's Introspection\"\n| \"An Altar of Beta-Carotene\"\n| \"A Machine Gun Without Ammo\"\n| \"If You Pour Out All the Lukewarm Water, You'll Be Left with Cold Water\"\n| \"A Shout in the Evening Like a Baby's First Cry\"\n| \"The Neck of an Hourglass: Ascending with You\"\n| \"A Requiem Can Sound Like a Hymn if You Listen Hard Enough\"\n| \"Our Tails, Afterimages Etched into Our Skulls\"\n| \"The More Colors are Mixed in Paint, the Blacker It Gets\"\n}}\n| Summary         = \n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber = 15\n | RelDate      = October 10, 2019<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.akitashoten.co.jp/comics/4253229034 |title=BEASTARS \u7b2c15\u5dfb |website=[[Akita Shoten]] |language=Japanese |accessdate=October 21, 2019 }}</ref>\n | ISBN         = 978-4-253-22903-6\n | LicensedRelDate = \u2014\n | LicensedISBN = \n| ChapterListCol1 = \n{{Numbered list|start=125\n| \"A Monster's Threatening Letter with a Noshi Attached\"\n| \"A Devil's Prayer is a Premonition of Bad Luck\"\n| \"Spots like a Mystical Beast Under a Disco Ball\"\n| \"A \"Danger Mixture\" Made to Counteract Against a Gas Outbreak\"\n| \"Jumping out of a Dream of an Annunciation\"\n| \"His Lead-Colored Prosthetic Leg is Sometimes Rainbow-Colored Under the Sun\"\n| \"A Forcibly-worn Flower Crown Made of Silver Vine\"\n| \"You Call Me by My Name as if I'm Already Dead\"\n| \"The High Tide Swallows the Beach's Sand\"\n}}\n| Summary         = \n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber = 16\n | RelDate      = December 6, 2019<ref>{{cite web |url