 expatriates in the United Arab Emirates]]\n[[Category:All Pakistan Muslim League politicians]]\n[[Category:Politicians from Karachi]]\n[[Category:Pakistani prisoners and detainees]]\n[[Category:Recipients of Nishan-e-Imtiaz]]\n[[Category:Recipients of Tamgha-e-Basalat]]\n[[Category:Defence and security analysts in Pakistan]]\n[[Category:Pakistani political party founders]]\n[[Category:Pakistani politicians convicted of crimes]]\n[[Category:Fugitives wanted by Pakistan]]\n[[Category:People sentenced to death in absentia]]\n[[Category:Heads of regimes who were later imprisoned]]\n", "name_user": "103.57.71.187", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pervez_Musharraf"}
